title: Calendar does not load
body:
**Describe the bug**
A clear and concise description of what the bug is.

**To Reproduce**
Steps to reproduce the behavior:
1. Open Teams for Linux
2. Click on the 'Calendar' button

**Expected behavior**
Calendar should be displayed

**Screenshots**
![Screenshot_20240815_071607](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5667a2b2-28ad-4efc-ab40-c878eb90486f)

 - Installation package [RPM]
